OL,3,CCabin crew recruitment drive launched
OL,4,Cby easyJet
OL,6,FAirline easyJet is launching a new
OL,7,Fcabin crew recruitment drive aimed at
OL,8,Fthe over 50s and people wanting to
OL,9,Fchange their mind about retirement.
OL,11,FThe campaign, called Returnships,
OL,12,Ffollows research suggesting that three
OL,13,Fin four people over the age of 50
OL,14,Fbelieved this was the perfect time for
OL,15,Fa new career.
OL,17,FTraining taster sessions will be
OL,18,Foffered at easyJet's London Gatwick
OL,19,Fcabin crew training centre.
