OL,3,CCabin crew recruitment drive launched
OL,4,Cby easyJet
OL,6,FPrevious recruitment campaigns have
OL,7,Fled to a big increase in new staff
OL,8,Fover the age of 50 and 60.
OL,10,FNew research by the airline among
OL,11,F2,000 over-50s showed that half have
OL,12,Fconsidered a new career.
OL,14,FMost respondents believed their age
OL,15,Fwould stop them being accepted for a
OL,16,Fcabin crew job and half mistakenly
OL,17,Fbelieved the role would mean being
OL,18,Faway from home for long periods of
OL,19,Ftime.
