OL,3,CCabin crew recruitment drive launched
OL,4,Cby easyJet
OL,6,FMichael Brown, director of cabin
OL,7,Fservices at easyJet, said: "Since
OL,8,Flaunching our campaign to encourage
OL,9,Fmore over-50s and career changers to
OL,10,Fbecome cabin crew, we've been
OL,11,Fdelighted by the fantastic response
OL,12,Fwith many more joining us and we want
OL,13,Fto see that continue.
OL,15,F"Being cabin crew can be a job for
OL,16,Fanyone with the skills, no matter
OL,17,Ftheir age, which is why it's important
OL,18,Fthat through our initiatives like our
OL,19,FReturnship campaign, we tackle
OL,20,Fmisconceptions about the job and
OL,21,Fbroaden horizons."
